reviews.text: Two huge chinese style yum cha places. A gym is available. Plus a cinema now!

Yue Xiu Plaza is a relatively small and run-down mall, but it sometimes suits our needs. However, the help desk is empty, and the eerie silence of this place as compared to other malls is rather disturbing. It seems more like a deserted mall, and I feel like walking into the mall under construction. However, being close to a bigger mall, it seems just behind.
Local shopping. Shops and Resturants
Just a local shopping centre
sneaker shops , snooker player center and restaurant etc.

reviews.text: 一般街坊商場 ,不是太多商舖開戶,有啲商舖仍是吉舖
有唔同種類嘅商店，環境幾好，交通亦都方便
雖然有戲院,但係安排上映電影次數太少,好看哪些甚少有得看,要去另一間才可以看到心水電影這間影院有待改進安排上映電影,座位都舒服
消閒好地方，地下圍繞多間多元食肆，平貴都有，豐儉由人。
